- Update to new xfce4-appfinder commands.
- Fix build against 3.9 Glade (bug #7334).
- Add shortcuts for XF86WWW and XF86Mail.
- Simplify the xfce_gdk_screen_get_active fucntion.
- Add xfce_dialog_show_help function.

